    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Be Mutiny is a turn-based strategy game about betrayal. You and your crew of swashbuckling pirates are on an epic treasure hunt - until it inevitably devolves into mutiny. But if you can survive the backstabbings and betrayals, the treasure will be yours!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067160/extras/c6f364a98991f7ad5193f8a025713213.poster.avif?t=1758671439\" width=1124 height=630 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067160/extras/c6f364a98991f7ad5193f8a025713213.webm?t=1758671439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067160/extras/c6f364a98991f7ad5193f8a025713213.mp4?t=1758671439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a cast of 11 colorful characters, each with their own claim for the legendary treasure. Throughout the game, you must choose which characters you recruit to your crew, and which characters you throw overboard.</p>",
